{"tid":1660063,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"Trump : 美國不是世界警察. 庫爾德族有時較ISIS更恐怖","createTime":"2019-10-17T09:47:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-18T04:28:29.000Z","uid":134071,"like":10,"dislike":99,"uniUserReply":81,"replies":[{"pid":"b7b4e7c034b1e1a5757b020ac6682e6cf11cc9cd","tid":1660063,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T09:47:05.000Z","msg":"睇怕果封信係由Mike Pence代筆....<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1486636-20191017.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1486636-20191017.htm&d=vw1niP5YtVVR3vfDaqqaAcorGdVmFuHsJRpnpeioS7U%3D&h=18639823\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1486636-20191017.htm&h=79b4b0d0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1486636-20191017.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n特朗普稱庫爾德族有時較恐怖分子更恐怖<br />\n2019-10-17 HKT 03:46<br />\n<br />\n<strong>美國總統特朗普表示，如果土耳其進入敘利亞，並不是美國問題，又形容庫爾德工人黨不是天使，有時較「伊斯蘭國」更加恐怖主義。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普在白宮表示，美國不是警察，是時候應該回家。</strong><br />\n<br />\n特朗普早前宣布美國從敘利亞撤軍。由於庫爾德工人黨長期顛覆土耳其，被美國、土耳其及歐盟列為恐怖組織。美國在敘利亞進行反恐期間，曾經與庫爾德族人合作。<br />\n<br />\n外界憂慮，現時的不穩定可能導致激進武裝再度活躍。"},{"pid":"31f3820307a21b5dfcfda0067be45a0cc63aadc3","tid":1660063,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T09:47:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PgjbDGh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPgjbDGh.jpg&h=e5447ac9&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"484666acd3d27415d5851168d6d23ca82ff384c6","tid":1660063,"uid":134071,"like":82,"dislike":9,"score":73,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T09:47:45.000Z","msg":"某D朋友唔駛再夢想美國會出兵香港...."},{"pid":"f86de2eccae710d8726a376ac040fce187798847","tid":1660063,"uid":91432,"like":87,"dislike":10,"score":77,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T09:48:40.000Z","msg":"Trump越來越靠唔住。佢老二Pence強硬好多。"},{"pid":"92ca3dede3f60de90f